msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-02-19-k8s-style-CEL-with-quarkus-chicory.adoc
msgid ""
"The injected `WasmQuarkusContext` bean configures `Instance.Builder` to use `MachineFactory` and `WasmModule`\n"
